          <section id="hong_kong">
            <h3>Hong Kong</h3>
            <p>When I was young, one of the countries we'd always visit would be
            Hong Kong. I always enjoyed our trips to Hong Kong as we'd get to spend
            time as a family and eat a lot of great food. Riding the train in Hong
            Kong was also nostalgic since it felt like every time I went there it
            would feel slightly different but still feel familiar as we'd been there
            a couple times already. Food in Hong Kong is really good. Service their
            is also very fast, like people there just operate quicker. Sometimes it
            might feel rude with how they treat you but I think it's really just
            how they do stuff there in Hong Kong. </p>
          </section>
        </div>

