        <div class="content">
          <section id="taiwan">
            <h3>Taiwan</h3>
            <p>Taiwan was also one of the countries I would also visit. Either it
            was with my family or with my friends on a study tour. Food there is
            also great. It feels like I could eat anything there and it would still
            feel like I'm eating good quality food. Although, there was a time when
            I was with my parents and we went to this food stall that had so many
            people lining up just to eat. So we also tried it, and at first I felt
            there was something off with the food but I just ate it either way.
            After a bit, my dad asked what we were eating and my mom said it was
            intestines. Needless to say, my sister, my dad, and I were quite shocked
            that we were eating intestines and even more shocked that there were
            that many people lined up for it. </p>
          </section>
        </div>

